OL,3,CMerseyside MPs join calls for a fairer
OL,4,Ccouncil tax system
OL,6,FMerseyside MPs have joined calls for a
OL,7,Ffairer council tax system, with many
OL,8,Fpeople across the region feeling the
OL,9,Fpinch of the cost of living crisis.
OL,11,FLiverpool Riverside, England's most
OL,12,Fdeprived constituency has rates that
OL,13,Fare double the national average.
OL,15,FAhead of the budget, campaigners are
OL,16,Fproposing a proportional property tax,
OL,17,Fwhere homeowners and landlords would
OL,18,Fpay a flat percentage of their current
OL,19,Fproperty value.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
