OL,3,CMerseyside MPs join calls for a fairer
OL,4,Ccouncil tax system
OL,6,FThose in favour of the changes say the
OL,7,Faverage household could save around
OL,8,F#800 a year.
OL,10,FAs a proportion of how much a property
OL,11,Fis worth, half of the top 10 highest
OL,12,Fareas for council tax in the United
OL,13,FKingdom are in the North West.
OL,15,FMerseyside MP Kim Johnson says it's
OL,16,Ftime for a change in the way council
OL,17,Ftax payments are distributed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
