OL,3,CMerseyside MPs join calls for a fairer
OL,4,Ccouncil tax system
OL,6,FLiverpool Riverside MP Kim Johnson
OL,7,Fsaid: "If you live in a #3million
OL,8,Fmansion in London, why are you paying
OL,9,Fless council tax proportionately than
OL,10,Fthose constituents in my Liverpool
OL,11,FRiverside constituency?
OL,13,F"The system is unfair. It needs to be
OL,14,Fchanged, and it needs to be looked at."
OL,16,FAndy Johnson rents a house in Welsh
OL,17,FStreets, Toxteth and has felt rents go
OL,18,Fup and public services be cut in the
OL,19,Feight years he has lived there.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
