OL,3,CMerseyside MPs join calls for a fairer
OL,4,Ccouncil tax system
OL,6,F"Everyone's always mentioning the
OL,7,Fcouncil tax, and what a struggle it is.
OL,9,F"It absolutely feeds into the cost of
OL,10,Fliving crisis and the pinch that
OL,11,Fpeople are feeling.
OL,13,F"At the school gates, you speak to
OL,14,Feveryone there and with everything
OL,15,Fthat you've got to find for shopping,
OL,16,Fbills, rent - the council tax is just
OL,17,Fa huge amount every month.
OL,19,F"We're finding it a struggle to meet.
OL,20,FAnd I'm sure other people are too."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
