OL,3,CMerseyside MPs join calls for a fairer
OL,4,Ccouncil tax system
OL,6,F"The North West is absolutely
OL,7,Fdisadvantaged with the current system.
OL,8,FProperties in Manchester, Liverpool,
OL,9,FBlackburn and Bolton often pay 1-2% of
OL,10,Ftheir property value each year in
OL,11,Fcouncil tax, whereas those in
OL,12,FWestminster pay 0.5%, 0.25%, 0.1%.
OL,14,FSo unfortunately, I would say that
OL,15,Fthose in the North West and the North
OL,16,FEast are deeply penalised.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
