OL,3,CMerseyside MPs join calls for a fairer
OL,4,Ccouncil tax system
OL,6,FThe Liverpool Acorn community union
OL,7,Fhelps people who are struggling to
OL,8,Fpay. It says more people in Liverpool
OL,9,Fare being referred to bailiffs than
OL,10,Fanywhere outside London.
OL,12,FThe Secretary at the Acorn Martin
OL,13,FMawdsley said: "It's such a big, big
OL,14,Fproblem that probably few people
OL,15,Factually realise because there is some
OL,16,Fsort of stigma attached to it. No one
OL,17,Fwants to admit it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
