OL,6,F"It's a big, big bill. So it's
OL,7,Factually not that shameful to be
OL,8,Fstruggling with it, especially these
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,FIt's one of the biggest bills that we
OL,12,Fpay, maybe after rents and mortgages.
OL,13,FAnd the problem is getting bigger and
OL,14,Fbigger."
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
